1. *Svrha* ovog sastanka je da se dogovorimo oko daljih koraka. (The *purpose* of this meeting is to agree on further steps.)
2. Molim te da mi objasniš koja je *svrha* ovog zadatka. (*Purpose*) (Please explain to me what is the *purpose* of this task.)
3. Kada budemo znali *svrhu* našeg putovanja, bićemo spremni za polazak. (When we know the *purpose* of our trip, we will be ready to depart.)
4. Nisam siguran u koju *svrhu* bi to bilo dobro uraditi. (I'm not sure for what *purpose* it would be good to do it.)
5. *Svrhom* ovog istraživanja je da se utvrdi uzrok problema. (*The purpose*) (The *purpose* of this research is to determine the cause of the problem.)
6. Ova oprema je napravljena *svrhom* olakšavanja rada. (*For the purpose*) (This equipment was made *for the purpose* of making work easier.)
7. Ona je uvek vredno radila *svrh* ostvarenja svog cilja. (*Towards the purpose*) (She has always worked hard *towards the purpose* of achieving her goal.)
8. *Svrhu* ove donacije smo usmerili ka pomoći deci u siromaštvu. (*The purpose*) (We have directed the *purpose* of this donation towards helping children in poverty.)
9. Naš cilj je da naš proizvod služi *svrsi* i da olakša život ljudima. (*Purpose*) (Our goal is for our product to serve a *purpose* and make people's lives easier.)
10. Nije važno da li postoji samo jedna *svrha* života ili više njih, važno je da je svako pronađe za sebe. (*Purpose*) (It doesn't matter whether there is only one *purpose* of life or several, it is important that everyone finds it for themselves.)